data.description: Discover the epitome of urban living in this exquisite 2-bedroom condo in Denver! You will be greeted by a captivating interior showcasing gleaming wood flooring, modern track lighting, soothing color palette, and floor-to-ceiling windows offering incredible city views, enhancing the overall sense of space throughout. The beautiful kitchen features wood cabinetry providing ample storage, tile counters, subway tile backsplash, sparkling stainless steel appliances, and a convenient pass-through window complete with a breakfast bar, ideal for casual dining or entertaining guests. Primary bedroom boasts a large mirrored-door closet and a private bathroom equipped with a tub/shower combo for added comfort. One of the condo's most impressive amenities is the rooftop Community pool, an oasis in the sky perfect for social gatherings and relaxation! This property is not just a residence; it's a lifestyle. What are you waiting for? This opportunity won't last long!
